import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { UnsplashService } from '../unsplash.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-unsplash', templateUrl: './unsplash.component.html', styleUrls: ['./unsplash.component.scss'] }) export class UnsplashComponent implements OnInit { [x: string]: Object; url = "string"; constructor(private unsplashService: UnsplashService) {} ngOnInit(){ this.unsplashService.getPhotos().subscribe(response => { this['photos'] = response; }); } }
